Fri Jun 12 10:20:42 UTC 2026 - Jan Engelhardt <jengelh@inai.de>

- Update to release 4.0.0
  * Added support for using OSCAR as external CAS (in addition to
    PARI/GP). By default, OSCAR support is automatically activated
    when Alnuth is loaded in GAP running inside OSCAR. In all other
    situations, PARI/GP remains the default.
  * Renamed `FactorsPolynomialPari` to `FactorsPolynomialAlnuth` to
    better reflect that it uses the active external CAS, not just
    PARI/GP (the old name is still supported as a synonym for now).
  * Replaced the old `AL_*` configuration globals by GAP's user
    preference system; the old variables are still used a fallback,
    but user preferences are preferred if set.

